data.description: Welcome home to your 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom haven. It offers a seamless blend of indoor and outdoor living, a study for added functionality and a layout designed for both entertaining and relaxation. With its generous lot size, proximity to nature, and thoughtful design, this home is an embodiment of comfort and style. Don't miss the opportunity to make it yours and embark on a new chapter of relaxation and comfort. Your new home is surrounded by shopping, restaurants, and walkable outdoor space. Imagine your pets having an outdoor oasis to frolic about while you look on from your covered patio, sipping on your most desired beverage.
